        <p class="">Located west of Pipe Springs National Monument, Masada Charter School serves any student, grades Kindergarten through 9th, within the geographic areas of Centennial Park, Colorado City, and Cane Beds. With our outstanding teaching staff, a dedicated support staff, and committed, involved parents, Masada Charter School maintains the highest standards for our students.</p>
        <div class="pom-container">
            <p class="">We hope you will use our website to learn more about our school and cheer on the successes of our students. Whether you are looking for student <a href="/Enrollment" title="" alt="" target="_self">registration</a> information, <a href="/Job-Openings" title="" alt="" target="_self">job openings</a>, or our school <a href="/Calendar" title="" alt="" target="_self">calendar</a> and events, you're welcome to contact us directly.</p>
