        <h2 class="">A Message from Our Administrators</h2>
        <p class="">On behalf of Masada Charter School, we welcome you to our website and hope you will find it a resource for school information as well as a place to which you'll return frequently for the many online resources it provides.</p>
        <div class="pom-container">
            <p class="">We're very proud of our school and its enthusiastic students, supportive parents and community, and dedicated teachers and support staff. By working together, we enjoy ever-increasing student achievement and instilling a love of learning in our students that will help them reach their individual goals and become successful, productive adults.</p>
            <div class="pom-container">
                <p class="">We look forward to being a part of our students' journeys as they achieve their individual goals. All of us here at Masada thank you for the opportunity to be a part of this adventure.</p>
